    "question": "¿Qué clientes tienen más tarjetas asociadas?",
    "sql": "SELECT\n  u.id AS client_id,\n  COUNT(c.id) AS num_cards\nFROM users u\nJOIN cards c ON c.client_id = u.id\nGROUP BY u.id\nORDER BY num_cards DESC\nLIMIT 50;",
